{"tid":1502561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋係咪失憶？一個二個咁快唔記得兄弟爬山","createTime":"2019-08-24T16:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T06:24:25.000Z","uid":88177,"like":87,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"da753a9b3b893f32eadf1e5dcb822634d8151016","tid":1502561,"uid":88177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:41:12.000Z","msg":"機場好，葵青荃好，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪全部唔記得咗一開始講好兄弟爬山，<br />\n核彈都唔割？</span></span><br />\n聽日打風，如果天氣唔好嘅咪入機場，<br />\n住附近嘅咪落葵青荃！！！<br />\n係咪真係全部失憶，定係連登已經比大量三毛侵佔？<br />\n<br />\n講多次<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n以眼還眼，兄弟爬山<br />\n和勇一體，核彈都唔撚割！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f585d39427b5b7cc0bbb15d47e9f8662cea094c","tid":1502561,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:41:26.000Z","msg":"有冇土瓜灣撚成間屋停哂電<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502558</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ab6c72b6b649f5f8d16c3290b338067c0aeffa4","tid":1502561,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4f585d39427b5b7cc0bbb15d47e9f8662cea094c","tid":1502561,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:41:26.000Z","msg":"有冇土瓜灣撚成間屋停哂電<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502558</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"呢個先啱<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ac957d9dce4804a8bdf1c384302f3ac872eb18c","tid":1502561,"uid":88177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ab6c72b6b649f5f8d16c3290b338067c0aeffa4","tid":150